{"type": "article", "id": 31908, "title": "网购奢侈品增加，以及，Nike Roshe推出花卉定制服务 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-09-07T02:37:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 32519, "name": "网购奢侈品"}, {"id": 32521, "name": "美国传媒集团"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 1746, "name": "Snapchat"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2910, "name": "Hugo Boss"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 32522, "name": "Hearest"}, {"id": 4703, "name": "刘雯"}, {"id": 13552, "name": "Jennifer Lawrence"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160907085949zwlAGxMsr8WuQ9fC.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/direct-internet-catalogue/chinas-luxury-consumer-moves-online-and-brands-follow-10483261/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>越来越多的中国消费者在网上购买奢侈品</b></a> | 商业咨询公司 L2 称，网购奢侈品占整个中国奢侈品市场的 5%，不过，它的销售额比去年上涨了 20 倍。越来越多的中国消费者在网上购买奢侈品，奢侈品牌也加大了对其电商的投入。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/joanna-coles-named-chief-content-officer-of-hearst-magazines-10521767/\" rel=\"nofollow\">世界最大的多元化传媒集团之一赫斯特任命新的杂志内容总监</a> </b>| Joanna Coles 将成为 Hearest 集团杂志部门新一任的内容总监。她曾于 2012 年开始担任 Hearest 旗下的著名杂志 Cosmopolitan 的总编辑。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/fashion-memopad/vogue-snapchat-channel-10522366/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Vogue 推出了 Snapchat 频道</b></a> | 每周二和周五，你都可以从 Snapchat 上的 Vogue 频道接受到来自 Vogue 的杂志内容。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/menswear-news/designer-luxury/hugo-boss-americas-gerrit-ruetze-anthony-lucia0522098-10522098/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hugo Boss 美国区现任 CEO Gerrit Ruetzel 将要离职</b></a> | Gerrit Ruetzel 于 2014 年担任 Hugo Boss 美国区 CEO，为了寻求其他的职业发展机会，他将于 9 月 30 日正式离职。Hugo Boss 任命 Anthony Lucia 为新的美国区 CEO，接任 Gerrit Ruetzel 的工作。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/watches/michael-kors-unveils-smartwatch-10520630/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michael Kors 推出了新一代的智能手表</a>，该系列在 Bradshaw 和 Dylan 的男女式手表风格的基础上，新增了一系列可替换的表带。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092357ThUMzIGpNBiQvHOu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092357oG0ti4SdRLmMnJyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092357vI8FU0YOyVWsuNAd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092357lRZX2ivfUKIxq9D4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092408xJGYOofnDuWasPwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609070924081rbg34Ea0eWAY5iI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092420R0nKWa6LZClpOjFo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092420vapW2gA8q6wdKHBi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092420PxIVutOn9DL2CbQY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/nike-roshe-two-nikeid-florals-pattern\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike Roshe Two NIKEiD 推出 Florals 图案订制服务</a>。这次 NIKEiD 推出的图案选择包括 Blue Lagoon、Bright Mandarin、Bright Crimson、Gym Red 及 Black，并可选择于鞋面及鞋腰上采用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092332ZTmkRjStPdxzUKch.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092332BIsuQgFop9tPmTci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609070923424kcImnL0V1DzPEaU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">刘雯身穿 Balenciaga 的秋季新款，亮相美国时尚电商 <a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/liu-wen-the-edit-2016-photos/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Net-a-Porter 的九月推荐刊物 The EDIT</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092139RcslHBgdymoPkGKM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274740\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092156UedoZAyIja89TxMK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274740\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092156eHUqQ4nkSItCMWlc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274740\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092208G1a2S0H6zyqkWsZu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274740\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092218Tar4EF8DiBpA7U6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274740\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092227UxbD3Scweg2uGfr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.274740\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092236KPUF6BWDj27uoHqv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092243VX0B9ahvlmb14k3U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/jennifer-lawrence-dior-campaign-fall-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jennifer Lawrence 代言 Dior 2016 秋季手袋系列</a>，重新定义时尚与优雅。这是 Jennifer 第二次成为 Dior 的代言人，上一次则是在 2013 年。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092057xUd1eTnL8CPGYVIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295573\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092110vnFDWGyJP2wrq3Th.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295573\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092110MsaD6hnpIguiXRTJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295573\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092116xuifbashH1K4m8nl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907092123XKZP6CapAFz7q9mg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p></p><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/9/nikelab-x-stone-island-windrunner-jacket\" rel=\"nofollow\">NikeLab 再度与意大利品牌 Stone Island 合作</a>，带来了全新的 Windrunner 夹克系列。该系列在确保轻盈透气的同时，也提供绝佳的防水防风功能。还可以通过弹力松紧带将夹克收纳至衣身上的左侧口袋，从而转换成一个斜挎包。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907091844hMR8dXgTaZinIFty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907091855dSb8PeMQfzvR7p1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907091856hJIvw17oF3ai9kUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907091856eQVq3swDtPz05Ocr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907091856YbPetmfrZijOksVB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160907091903D8ObY02TAyQhVZJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}